ike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:28:04.000Z","msg":"18/10(Fri)： 5點港大反警暴集會，7點18區面具人鏈<br />\n19/10(Sat)： 7點半遮打國際人道救援祈禱會<br />\n20/10(Sun)： 1點半九龍民陣大遊行<br />\n21/10(Mon)： 7點元朗靜坐<br />\n25/10(Fri)： 朝早7點九龍港島和你返工"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T05:04:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e50639a1a5db06e3bc5c261ebcef68cb77c4321c","tid":1657284,"uid":106368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2efed744617f8961096b0303a0f0a02959daa747","tid":1657284,"uid":270374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:30:12.000Z","msg":"<strong>英、德、日、台版人權法案</strong><br />\n<br />\n以海外活動來說，300萬不算多，大家考慮下。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>香港眾志國際眾籌計劃</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25B1%258C%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project%2F&d=TC1Ad7l9MtPLjBCdpR1LVlNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=f50d26d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/</a><br />\n<br />\n新一階段工作為期兩年，除繼續經營美國網絡外，我們亦將集中德國、英國、日本、台灣等四大重點國家，拓展我們的連結及遊說網絡，當中德國是過去多次就人權問題發聲的歐盟成員國之一、英國是《中英聯合聲明》簽署國、台灣則同樣是威權中國下的命運共同體，而日本乃東亞最具軟實力、近年相當關注中國影響的國家。<br />\n<br />\n新一階段國際遊說工作為期兩年，眾籌金額300萬，包括：<br />\n【海外網絡】資助海外港人進行遊說，在重點國家建立長期遊說網絡（約50萬）<br />\n【主動外訪】針對外國國會及政府機關，主動出擊進行策略性外訪（約100萬）【🔎訪港考察】邀請議員及社運組織來港考察，壯大香港與其他公民社會（約50萬）<br />\n【研究團隊】聘請本地研究團隊，為遊說及倡議工作提供法律研究和研究支援（約100萬）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T05:05:09.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c4ad398935616f3c424055f3a49b6af7013cba2","tid":1657284,"uid":106368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T05:06:31.000Z","msg":"其實好奇長文係咪冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4b6e4e5d3f9a7430ae2169440c5105069484d0c","tid":1657284,"uid":106368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T05:07:08.000Z","msg":"再自推10次<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96ea1c6b4765e9779047fdf4c51cc1a84f8bae43","tid":1657284,"uid":106368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T05:07:22.000Z","msg":"2<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"792af97c43b35d8346ac3a46a4f89fac9e7d7453","tid":1657284,"uid":106368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T05:07:32.000Z","msg":"3<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"491eb263317a404465d9fcd7835e205d1b7dd444","tid":1657284,"uid":106368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T05:07:45.000Z","msg":"4<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b547c9168e0d3444352601a20d8f1988fc2658a","tid":1657284,"uid":106368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T05:07:57.000Z","msg":"5<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfb748558e7cad4cf95aeefa97b8a5ca14398750","tid":1657284,"uid":106368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T05:08:08.000Z","msg":"6<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e5f68ee4ed2b3e8fb3a0e6cc46bd78f3d05107a","tid":1657284,"uid":106368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T05:08:21.000Z","msg":"7<img src=\